Word Count
Ruby BDD/Sinatra Exercise for Epicodus Code Review, August 7, 2015

By Janice V. Dunn

Description
This application counts the number of time a specific word occurs in a phrase.

Setup
Clone this repository
Open a simple HTTP server in the top level of the cloned directory
Run the Sinatra server
Then open your web browser of choice to localhost:4567

